---
import {Image} from 'astro:assets';
import Avatar from '../assets/avatar.webp';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
        title="About Patrick Scheid - Senior Software Engineer"
        description="Senior Software Engineer at DeepL with a background spanning data science, product management, and engineering leadership. Based in Munich."
        pageClass="page-about"
>
    <article class="prose">
        <div class="about-header">
            <Image src={Avatar} alt="Patrick Scheid" class="avatar" width={200} height={200}/>
            <h1>About Me</h1>
        </div>

        <p>
            Hi, I'm Patrick Scheid, a Senior Software Engineer at DeepL based in Munich. I work at the intersection
            of AI research and product development, turning cutting-edge research into practical, user-facing features.
        </p>

        <h2>What I Do</h2>
        <p>
            At DeepL, I work on the Editor Team, bridging AI research and real-world editing tools. Previously, I
            was on the Document Translation Team, where I drove stability and performance improvements through
            technical analysis and solution design. My work involves close collaboration with AI researchers to
            integrate new capabilities into production systems.
        </p>

        <h2>Background</h2>
        <p>
            My career spans multiple disciplines, and each role has shaped how I approach building products today:
        </p>

        <div class="timeline">
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h3>Senior Software Engineer</h3>
                    <p>Combining all perspectives to ship impactful products at the intersection of AI and engineering.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h3>Product Owner</h3>
                    <p>Shaping APIs into API-as-a-Product offerings, balancing user value with business impact.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h3>Scrum Master</h3>
                    <p>Facilitating team dynamics, iterative delivery, and continuous improvement.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h3>Software Engineer</h3>
                    <p>Designing scalable cloud backends, microservices, and infrastructure with Kubernetes, PostgreSQL, and Go.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h3>Data Scientist</h3>
                    <p>Extracting insights from complex data and building data-driven solutions.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2>How I Work</h2>
        <p>
            I believe the best solutions emerge when teams understand the "why" behind what they build. I combine
            technical depth with a strong emphasis on collaboration, clear communication, and pragmatic
            problem-solving. I care about getting the right things done well — not just shipping fast.
        </p>

        <h2>Let's Connect</h2>
        <p>
            I'm always open to conversations about technology, product development, and team leadership —
            whether that's exchanging ideas, exploring collaborations, or discussing new opportunities.
            Feel free to reach out!
        </p>
    </article>
</Layout>

<style>
    .about-header {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 2em 0;
    }

    .avatar {
        width: 200px;
        height: 200px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        margin: 0 auto 1em;
        display: block;
        box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
    }

    .prose {
        margin: auto;
        padding: 1em;
        color: var(--color-text);
    }

    .timeline {
        position: relative;
        padding-left: 2.5rem;
        margin: 1.5em 0 2em;
    }

    .timeline::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        left: 0.55rem;
        top: 0.25rem;
        bottom: 0.25rem;
        width: 2px;
        background: var(--color-border);
    }

    .timeline-item {
        position: relative;
        padding-bottom: 1.5em;
    }

    .timeline-item:last-child {
        padding-bottom: 0;
    }

    .timeline-dot {
        position: absolute;
        left: -2.25rem;
        top: 0.35rem;
        width: 14px;
        height: 14px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: var(--color-accent);
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px var(--color-bg);
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .timeline-content h3 {
        margin: 0 0 0.25em;
        font-size: 1.1em;
    }

    .timeline-content p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--color-text-muted);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }
</style>
